31-JAN-1999 Jeroen Nijhof (J.H.B.Nijhof@aston.ac.uk)

	* New maintainer

	* Removed the dos and unix batch files for generating
	  the mf-files, and replaced them with tex files
	  doing the same thing, in directory make-mf. Use rounded
	  magstep sizes (10.95, 24.88, etc.)

	* Under holin, changed the mf files in ready-mf and
	  the driver files generating them to use rounded magstep
	  sizes as well.

	* of the latex files, changed fontmath.cfg (let it read 
	  fontmath.ltx), fonttext.cfg (test for case of OMLenc.def
	  etc.), and sauttext.fd (removed T1 font definitions).
          removed obsolete dcstdedt.tex. Added sizes 29.86 pt and 
	  35.83 pt to saut*.fd.
	
