19-JUL-1996 J\"org Knappen (knappen@vkpmzd.kph.uni-mainz.de)

        * Version 2.4

        * Fixed the cap_ess formula in c-cmmi for sizes >12pt

        * Fixed the formula for lower.comma_depth in c-cmcsc
          for sizes \ge 10pt. This change affects the metric
          (depth of lowercase q) but not the checksum.

        * Fixed several typos and bad line breaks as reported
          by Michael Blaustein <mblauste@CapAccess.org>

        * Brought documentation up to date, mentioning the contribution
          of Hubert Holin

        * Finally decided not to support the Knuthian local
          extra cm fonts; imho the stability of the established 
          Sauter distribution is not worth breaking

